  "body": "# Rationale\r\nI'd like to have numerous Wallets, with easily identifiable names.  Rather than a bunch of UTC...   Then I wouldn't need to keep a manual directory record of the intended purpose of each wallet.\r\n\r\n# Implementation\r\nCreate:\r\n--walletname\r\npersonal.newAccount(\"notmyrealpassword\") --walletname FriendlyWalletName\r\n\r\nAre you willing to implement this feature?\r\nBeyond the scope of my experience.\r\n\r\nhttps://geth.ethereum.org/docs/interface/command-line-options",
